{"tid":1595013,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"心理調節：不再因為憤怒而走上街","createTime":"2019-09-26T00:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T08:22:42.000Z","uid":274371,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe2b1587e133388169d8329fdeadd88654490b8","tid":1595013,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:26:14.000Z","msg":"不再因為憤怒而走上街。<br />\n<br />\n如果要有手足受傷流血、被爆頭、被自殺，我哋先感受到短暫嘅怒火，繼而走上街、行動，咁唔係另一種<span style=\"color: red;\">人血饅頭</span>咩？我哋消費緊手足嘅痛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n走上街、行動嘅出發點，必須係因為對光復香港嘅堅持、對抗衡暴政嘅執著，咁先可以有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>持久力</strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，我哋一齊走落去！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港人<br />\n加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"023f4afb5ac39af04d06cb176091e158a76a9e52","tid":1595013,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:26:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62e6e5aba423ef22de46ea1cc882dddefa122b2c","tid":1595013,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:26:41.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c77bbc8ea3aff907cd6957d8d53ff5943def7338","tid":1595013,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:26:47.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"7d18d061b454905f7eb014429ac699977ee11dcf","tid":1595013,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:26:51.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"0c86514d9ff2e4f3be297cfdf89b1549aad5361a","tid":1595013,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T00:26:54.000Z","msg":"推啦幫你"},{"pid":"82beb605a48ee856d0335309d0f8777dfa37ebfe","tid":15